numberOne = int(input("Starting number? "))
numberTwo = int(input("Ending number? "))
Numbers = range(numberOne, numberTwo + 1)
Sum = sum(Numbers)
print("")

for counter in range (numberOne, numberTwo + 1):
  if (numberOne >= numberTwo) or (numberTwo < numberOne):
    print("Ending number must be greater than", numberOne)
    numberTwo = (int(input("Ending number? ")))
    Numbers = range(numberOne, numberTwo + 1)
    Sum = sum(Numbers)
    print ("The sum of numbers from", numberOne, "to", numberTwo, "is", Sum)
    break
  elif (numberOne < numberTwo):
    print ("The sum of numbers from", numberOne, "to", numberTwo, "is", Sum)
    break
  elif (numberOne == numberTwo):
    break
